{"tid":279833,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一條概率請教大家","createTime":"2017-06-11T15:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T16:28:01.000Z","uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48f5f458b27937c43336b5c115520d0c8166ba61","tid":279833,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"舉個日常既事例先，，有5個單位用同一條排水管咁啦。。<br />\n1。咁係我開水期間其他人都會開水既機會率係幾多。<br />\n2。其他人開水期間，我唔會開水既機會率又係幾多。"},{"pid":"9922b1cc61523dae3f90f9214a073cc4b5e5e4e2","tid":279833,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"你都要比d bg infomation 先得嫁"},{"pid":"cf765c5dc6d528097e3e1fd36c126bc9d0a63e61","tid":279833,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91518cbb1013fa41278846ffefb10341b3e4dca","tid":279833,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"例如咩資訊，仲味學"},{"pid":"9329eb1bc55bfac056c76865ef5deea94846270c","tid":279833,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"0-1"},{"pid":"2691a86ccd67acf5eb1ca1480a9b197bbabcee3b","tid":279833,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"計嚟做乜<br />\n概率除咗用嚟戒賭之外我諗唔到有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e079d5c0051a3660304d75be2c9f7ebf788427","tid":279833,"uid":23815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如咩資訊，仲味學</blockquote><br />\n味您老母咩<br />\n中五都未讀仲好意思咁大聲講出黎"},{"pid":"8ebc222741f7e296416cf164fbbdfb034a1d9250","tid":279833,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>例如咩資訊，仲味學</blockquote><br />\n味您老母咩<br />\n中五都未讀仲好意思咁大聲講出黎</blockquote><br />\n深深體會到乜嘢叫「後生是原罪」"},{"pid":"43cccc41853cb6bf1367761715b27f7f072f595b","tid":279833,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>例如咩資訊，仲味學</blockquote><br />\n味您老母咩<br />\n中五都未讀仲好意思咁大聲講出黎</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，我都想學，我間仆街學校，有次中文唔小心衰左，＜＜用中文分班，分左同啲差既人一齊，果時佢啲數係咩班至咩班學進階數，而差啲既學番基礎數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己都有自習，但係唔明"},{"pid":"f680a201e9dbedeaf1a2763ea7f3f203ab3dce91","tid":279833,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"當係你地日常沖涼咁既用水頻率。大概咁作0-1"},{"pid":"35f8ad7b159443bede9574d436939621319eae49","tid":279833,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e2efeec98aff8e7c1b520b27db8d5de5c92979a","tid":279833,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你開水既機率係咩又唔講 其他人開水既機率又唔講<br />\n點計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當正常人平時1日1-3次咁，5個單位都差唔多，是但代入數(正常頻率)沖涼既次數，黎計"},{"pid":"6914083f86115aec37f6175ad0a06e104484724b","tid":279833,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"其他人係指所有人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}